---
import { whyChooseReasons } from '../data/site-data';
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-bgLight/50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-primary mb-6 font-bold">Por que escolher o Dr. Jony?</h2>
      <div class="h-px bg-secondary/30 w-16 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 font-light">
        Quando se trata da sua saúde, escolher um profissional vai além do currículo. 
        Ofereço um cuidado centrado em você, valorizando a escuta e a segurança.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento Grid Container -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 md:grid-rows-2 gap-6 auto-rows-[minmax(250px,auto)]">
      
      <!-- Bento Item 1: Large Featured (Spans 2 columns on desktop) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 bg-primary text-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden group shadow-sm border border-primary/20">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid-pattern.svg')] opacity-10 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-white/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-white"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">{whyChooseReasons[0] || 'Experiência e Precisão'}</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 font-light max-w-md">Aliamos anos de experiência clínica com tecnologia de ponta para diagnósticos precisos e tratamentos eficazes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bento Item 2: Tall Image (Spans 2 rows on desktop) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 relative overflow-hidden shadow-sm group">
        <img src="/dr-jony-profile.webp" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105" alt="Atendimento Médico" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/90 via-slate-900/40 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-8 z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-secondary text-white flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border border-white/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-2">{whyChooseReasons[1] || 'Atendimento Humanizado'}</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-light">Uma consulta sem pressa, onde você é ouvida, respeitada e tem todas as suas dúvidas esclarecidas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bento Item 3: Secondary Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-3">Valorização do Tempo</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">Atendimento particular organizado para minimizar atrasos e respeitar a sua rotina diária.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bento Item 4: Accent Tile -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 bg-slate-800 text-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-700 flex flex-col justify-center">
         <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white/10 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-3">{whyChooseReasons[2] || 'Suporte Contínuo'}</h3>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed">Estou acessível para orientações ao longo de todo o seu tratamento e especialmente durante o pré-natal.</p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
